channel.title: Willing to make vB or IPB forums
channel.description:
If you have a server (RS preferably) I'd be willing to make a forum and be very active on it vB if you can find offshore hosting, but IPB would work too,
Experience:
- ExAdmin at Die Hard Gaming (3,000+ users) -Ex Owner at Uc Gaming, not very successful but forums were flawless
and a bunch of other servers.
Message me with details. Email: theelementuhl@gmail.com Skype: Martin.Jeezy
Thanks.
